name: FM4 FULL FACE MASK M/L
description:
For the user of a ventilation system, the key elements for determining the appropriateness are comfort and performance of the facepiece and the FM4 Scott Safety offers the highest levels acceptance in the user.

Comfort is enhanced with silicone sealing edge LSR and unlimited field of vision (98%)
The lateral connection improves comfort and balance
Full mask in three sizes, is also certified for use with the Pro2000 filters.
Compatible with Proflow, Duraflow and Powered Air Systems
CE certification according to EN 12942 TM3 and AS / NZS1716-P3.

name: RFF4000 VISION FULL FACE MASK
description:
Vision is Scott Health & Safety's latest high performance full face respirator. It provides an unsurpassed field of vision and guarantees levels of protection and maintainability that set new standards in the industry. Its shape maximises the sealing area on the widest population of faces and thereby minimises pressure points.

Standards
EN136
EN12942 TM3 (RFF4000 only)
AS/NZ1715

For use with Scott Pro2000 filters.

description: When the health officials said healthy people should wear facemasks, we started building prototypes until we made the perfect one for athletes. The 3-Layer system features; Layer 1: Spacer fabric its light with air pockets to create structure, so it can stay off your mouth and nose for better airflow.
